  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prolongation of mechanical ventilation poses serious personal and financial threats to
      healthcare consumers.

      The investigators objectives are create and implement an multidisciplinary evidenced-based
      ventilator-weaning protocol to assess whether a systematic approach compared with the
      physician's judgment only decreases time spent on the ventilator, complications of mechanical
      ventilation and length of stay in critical care unit.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
